com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kamala-harris-taylor-swift-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kamala-harris-taylor-swift-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kamala-harris-taylor-swift-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>表示，她“非常自豪”在即将到来的美国总统选举中得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>的支持。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/pop-not-dirty-word-taylor-swift-finally-got-political-why-now-2387931">流行不是一个肮脏的词：泰勒·斯威夫特终于开始政治化了。是什么让她花了这么长时间？</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位流行巨星本月早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">支持了副总统和民主党提名人</a>，并在一份声明中写道，“她为权利和事业而战，我认为需要一位战士来捍卫它们”。</p><p>此后，哈里斯对斯威夫特的大力支持做出了回应——据报道，这导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-has-caused-a-500-per-cent-increase-in-voter-registration-3793306">选民登记人数增加了 500%</a> 。</p><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u9-cjwpthz4" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-component="link" data-source="inlineLink" data-type="externalLink" data-ordinal="1">《连线》杂志“</a></em>回答网络上搜索次数最多的问题”视频专题采访时，副总统对谷歌搜索“卡马拉·哈里斯·泰勒·斯威夫特”做出了回应，这位政客透露，她“非常自豪能得到网络的支持”。流行图标。</p><p> “她是一位令人难以置信的艺术家，”哈里斯说。 “我真的很尊重她在职业生涯中坚持自己认为正确的事情的勇气。”</p><p>这位总统候选人还开玩笑说，虽然他们的政治立场一致，但她和这位“Eras”明星在 NFL 方面并没有太多共同点。</p><p> “但去年我们在超级碗比赛中站在了不同的一边，”她说道，这是对斯威夫特对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-travis-kelce-super-bowl-2024-champion-3585849">男友特拉维斯·凯尔斯 (Travis Kelce) 赢得堪萨斯城酋长队冠军</a>的支持的认可。</p><p> “我是 [旧金山] 49 人队的球迷，但谁会对忠于他们球队的人生气，对吧？”哈里斯说。</p><p>斯威夫特在 Instagram 上发表的长篇认可帖子——她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-the-first-trump-vs-harris-presidential-debate-it-was-like-watching-muhammad-ali-3792635">哈里斯和共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普之间的第一次总统辩论</a>后分享了这篇帖子——也将副总统描述为“一位稳重、有天赋的领导人，我相信，如果我们能够在这个国家取得更多成就，我们的领导是平静而不是混乱”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_wtAOKOW1z/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06