 System Of A Down 的 Shavo Odadjian 表示他对新材料的“大门永远敞开” https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-downs-shavo-odadjian-says-his-door-is-always-open-for-new-material-3795820?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=系统-of-a-downs-shavo-odadjian-说他的门永远为新材料敞开Laura MolloySat, 21 Sep 2024 08:04:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3795820 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="沙沃·奥达吉安.图片来源：凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他接着说，乐队的新音乐“没有出现”，“真是太遗憾了”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-downs-shavo-odadjian-says-his-door-is-always-open-for-new-material-3795820">System Of A Down 的 Shavo Odadjian 表示，他的“大门永远敞开”，新材料</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="沙沃·奥达吉安.图片来源：凯文·温特/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Shavo-Odadjian.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/system-of-a-down">System Of A Down</a>的 Shavo Odadjian 在一次新的采访中透露，他愿意与乐队一起录制新材料。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/system-of-a-down-serj-tankian-memoir-3764456">System Of A Down 的 Serj Tankian：“我们生活在一个不公正的世界”</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队的最后一张唱片《Hypnotize》和《Mezmerize》于 2005 年发行。次年，他们宣布暂停演出，一直持续到 2011 年，当时他们在一系列欧洲音乐节上重聚。尽管此后他们断断续续地巡演，但在新音乐方面，他们只发行了两首单曲： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/system-of-a-down-share-first-new-songs-in-15-years-protect-the-land-and-genocidal-humanoidz-2810433">2020 年的《Protect the Land》和《Genocidal Humanoidz》</a> 。</p><p>现在，奥达吉安表示，他创作新音乐的“大门永远敞开”。 “我有一百个即兴重复段在等着，如果他们需要我的话，”贝斯手告诉播客<em><a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/7CA7YrvdOnmU3dJ6IgQYC4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Loudwire Nights</a> 。</em></p><p>他接着说，乐队的新音乐“没有出现”，“真是太遗憾了”，因为我们可以做很多事情。听着，我们进去了，四年前我们做了两首歌。他们听起来怎么样，伙计。我的意思是，那可能是一张那种狗屎的专辑。我们甚至可以写更疯狂的歌曲。那很快。达伦（Daron）带来了其中的一些——繁荣，繁荣，繁荣——这首歌就完成了；大约是两天。</p><p> “想象一下，如果它开始创作真正的音乐并关心专辑。因为我们创作专辑。我们不是词曲作者。我们是制作专辑的词曲作者。这一切都与专辑的构成有关。”</p><p>他还表示乐队仍然“彼此保持冷静”，并说道：“我们走在舞台上。我们彼此相爱。所以总会有这样的事。我想一直和他们一起表演。你永远不知道，兄弟。我总是会让那扇门开着。不应该被关闭。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_f-aA3pC3N/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; b